---
title: Smart Crunchy Clementine Chicken Thighs Salad with Creamy Sesame Dressing
description: The perfect salad can be achieved! This one is proof – it has a fresh and crunchy base, juicy clementines, soy marinated chicken and a nutty dressing. Toasted slivered almonds adds crunch and a retro vibe.

